snippet.title: SHRAPNEL Extraction Packs Trailer | Early Video Game Access?! 👀
snippet.description:
Prepare for Earthfall! Extraction Packs w/ early access to FPS Extraction Shooter, SHRAPNEL, are Available NOW ➡ https://www.shrapnel.com/marketplace 

SHRAPNEL is the 1st blockchain-enabled AAA customizable First Person Shooter (FPS) video game to be owned by players.
